gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 114, Jazz 104
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Anthony Edwards' 32 points, seven rebounds and eight assists, the Timberwolves defeated the Jazz, 114-104. Naz Reid (17 points, four rebounds) and Nickeil Alexander-Walker (13 points, four rebounds, five assists) added a combined 30 points for the Timberwolves in the victory, while Lauri Markkanen tallied 22 points and 12 rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Timberwolves have won three straight games as they improve to 47-21 on the season, while the Jazz fall to 29-39.
